1
00:00:07,007 --> 00:00:10,385
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [narrator] <i>Previously on</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Rick and Morty:
- Jerry, I had sex with your wife.</font>

2
00:00:11,136 --> 00:00:13,222
<font face="Serif" size="18">I did it! I fixed portal travel!</font>

3
00:00:13,305 --> 00:00:15,974
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Jack the Ripper, at your service.
- Cool!</font>

4
00:00:16,058 --> 00:00:17,142
<font face="Serif" size="18">This happened too?</font>

5
00:00:17,226 --> 00:00:19,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'm pregnant.
- Honey, she's just like you!</font>

6
00:00:19,603 --> 00:00:21,939
<font face="Serif" size="18">- It's raining meatballs!
- Okay, something is...</font>

7
00:00:22,022 --> 00:00:25,526
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jerry Smith died doing what he loved.
Getting stung by bees.</font>

8
00:00:25,609 --> 00:00:29,321
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Off.
- Off what? Have some respect. It's Dad's funeral.</font>

9
00:00:29,404 --> 00:00:31,281
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm going to name you Jerry Jr.</font>

10
00:00:31,365 --> 00:00:33,784
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thanks for solving that murder, guys.
Here's a skateboard.</font>

11
00:00:33,867 --> 00:00:36,119
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Thanks, Tony Hawk! What?
- Morty, say you'll marry me!</font>

12
00:00:36,203 --> 00:00:37,496
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Just say yes!
- Yes?</font>

13
00:00:37,579 --> 00:00:38,580
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay.</font>

14
00:00:38,664 --> 00:00:41,333
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Rick, do you promise to--
- I do, and for our honeymoon let's go</font>

15
00:00:41,416 --> 00:00:43,835
<font face="Serif" size="18">- to a sealed chamber lined with ionized deuterium.
- Why?</font>

16
00:00:43,919 --> 00:00:47,214
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because the charge acts as a narrative decelerant.
Morty, none of this is real.</font>

17
00:00:47,297 --> 00:00:49,466
<font face="Serif" size="18">We're in a "previously on" spiral.
Clear your head.</font>

18
00:00:49,550 --> 00:00:51,218
<font face="Serif" size="18">- After all that's happened?
- No.</font>

19
00:00:51,301 --> 00:00:54,721
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm innocent! I didn't release those bees!
I love Jerry!</font>

20
00:00:54,805 --> 00:00:56,348
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What'd I just say?
- When?</font>

21
00:00:56,431 --> 00:00:59,101
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, great execution.
Let's go back to the chamber.</font>

22
00:00:59,184 --> 00:01:01,937
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now repeat after me, Morty:
"Next time on <i>Rick and Morty."</i></font>

23
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:04,022
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Next time on <i>Rick and Morty?
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- [narrator] <i>No.</i></font>

24
00:01:04,106 --> 00:01:05,649
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Previously on</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Rick and Morty:</font>

25
00:01:05,732 --> 00:01:09,111
<font face="Serif" size="18">ignore it, Morty. "Next time on <i>Rick and Morty."
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">It counteracts his toxins.</font>

26
00:01:09,194 --> 00:01:11,530
<font face="Serif" size="18">Next time on <i>Rick and Morty.</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Whose toxins?</font>

27
00:01:11,613 --> 00:01:14,324
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Previous Leon] Hey, stop it!
- Previous Leon! Grab him!</font>

28
00:01:14,408 --> 00:01:15,409
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh no!</font>

29
00:01:15,492 --> 00:01:18,078
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hold on tight, Morty!
We gotta get through the opening titles!</font>

30
00:01:18,161 --> 00:01:19,496
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Morty] Opening titles of what?</font>

31
00:01:19,580 --> 00:01:21,790
<font face="Serif" size="18">- We're in space!
- [Previous Leon] Let go of me! Ow!</font>

32
00:01:22,499 --> 00:01:25,961
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, my God! Oh, my God!</font>

33
00:01:26,044 --> 00:01:27,337
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

34
00:01:28,755 --> 00:01:31,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Morty] What planet is this?
- [Rick] Cover your eyes on this part.</font>

35
00:01:31,633 --> 00:01:33,677
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Morty] Oh, my God, it's a giant squirrel!</font>

36
00:01:34,511 --> 00:01:38,515
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why are we dressed like old-timey people?
What the hell's going on?</font>

37
00:01:39,266 --> 00:01:41,184
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Rick] Oh!
- [Morty] Why is my dad in a suit?</font>

38
00:01:41,268 --> 00:01:43,604
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Rick] Best episode!
- [Morty] Why am I butter?</font>

39
00:01:43,687 --> 00:01:45,397
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick] Okay, we're almost through.</font>

40
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,523
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all shouting]</font>

41
00:01:47,941 --> 00:01:48,817
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ow!</font>

42
00:01:52,362 --> 00:01:54,364
<font face="Serif" size="18">- And we're back!
- [Previous Leon] Stop!</font>

43
00:01:54,448 --> 00:01:56,908
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What just happened? Why was there music?
- Let go of me!</font>

44
00:01:58,035 --> 00:02:01,121
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because of this conceptual little piece of shit!
Grab his feet!</font>

45
00:02:01,204 --> 00:02:04,374
<font face="Serif" size="18">If we have opening titles,
does that mean that we're a...</font>

46
00:02:04,458 --> 00:02:08,128
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let your body purge the meta-venom.
Don't succumb to his pointless self-aware bullshit.</font>

47
00:02:08,211 --> 00:02:09,921
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's not pointless, it's cool.</font>

48
00:02:10,464 --> 00:02:12,174
<font face="Serif" size="18">- He's got a gun!
- Eat lead, pussy!</font>

49
00:02:14,259 --> 00:02:16,470
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, no, no! Fuck!</font>

50
00:02:19,097 --> 00:02:20,682
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Son of a...
- Did he use a portal?</font>

51
00:02:20,766 --> 00:02:24,102
<font face="Serif" size="18">He wishes. He wriggled back to the meta layer
through a hole in the fourth wall.</font>

52
00:02:24,186 --> 00:02:25,854
<font face="Serif" size="18">Put these on and help me find it.</font>

53
00:02:27,981 --> 00:02:31,109
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I don't like this, Rick.
- You shouldn't. It's not a likable premise.</font>

54
00:02:31,193 --> 00:02:33,236
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's funny when I do a nod to the viewers, but--</font>

55
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,739
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What viewers?
- That's the right attitude, Morty.</font>

56
00:02:35,822 --> 00:02:40,243
<font face="Serif" size="18">A few carefree verbal asides, always by me.
None of this Season 3 <i>Moonlighting</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> shit.</font>

57
00:02:40,327 --> 00:02:42,245
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Okay, here it is.
- You're going to patch it?</font>

58
00:02:42,329 --> 00:02:47,167
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, he subverted actual reality, Morty.
He needs to be put down like a rabid dog.</font>

59
00:02:55,342 --> 00:02:58,595
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Ow! Fuck!
- No, you don't wanna wear those over here.</font>

60
00:03:00,263 --> 00:03:03,600
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Maybe he went down that road?
- No, no. if he took that, he'd end up a hero.</font>

61
00:03:03,684 --> 00:03:05,227
<font face="Serif" size="18">Damn it, Rick. I don't like this.</font>

62
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:08,063
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Is this whole place just--
- A bunch of groan-inducing wordplay</font>

63
00:03:08,146 --> 00:03:10,107
<font face="Serif" size="18">for seven TV critics that won't even enjoy it?</font>

64
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:13,276
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's worse than you think.
We're basting in meta radiation right now.</font>

65
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,237
<font face="Serif" size="18">Our credibility is being permanently eroded.</font>

66
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:18,490
<font face="Serif" size="18">Every second we spend here is the equivalent
to 10 <i>Space Jam</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> cameos.</font>

67
00:03:18,573 --> 00:03:21,702
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You should have thought of that previously.
- Get him!</font>

68
00:03:27,541 --> 00:03:30,252
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, no! Bless me, Heavenly Father,
for you will save me.</font>

69
00:03:30,335 --> 00:03:33,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Now I feel bad. Let's just get out of here.
- Because he prays?</font>

70
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:35,298
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know Hitler was Catholic, right?</font>

71
00:03:35,924 --> 00:03:36,967
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm here, Leon.</font>

72
00:03:37,551 --> 00:03:40,303
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay. He apparently prays very well.</font>

73
00:03:40,387 --> 00:03:43,140
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Time for you two to meet the Lord.
- That's okay, we're good.</font>

74
00:03:43,223 --> 00:03:46,727
<font face="Serif" size="18">Treat it like a bear attack.
Just walk backwards and make yourself look big.</font>

75
00:03:46,810 --> 00:03:51,398
<font face="Serif" size="18">I love a good refusal of the call. Hello, Rick.</font>

76
00:03:51,481 --> 00:03:55,444
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Hello. Amish Juggler?
- His name is Story Lord.</font>

77
00:03:55,527 --> 00:03:59,406
<font face="Serif" size="18">Story Lord? Listen, trust me,
take Amish Juggler. You can have it.</font>

78
00:03:59,489 --> 00:04:02,868
<font face="Serif" size="18">Story Lord. Rick, he's the villain
from that toy train I bought you.</font>

79
00:04:02,951 --> 00:04:06,830
<font face="Serif" size="18">Very good, Morty. The fictional versions
of you trapped me in a Bible show for children,</font>

80
00:04:06,913 --> 00:04:11,293
<font face="Serif" size="18">but I used make-believe Christ
to transcend fiction and enter meta-reality.</font>

81
00:04:11,376 --> 00:04:13,712
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now I'm the one doing the trapping.</font>

82
00:04:13,795 --> 00:04:15,964
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Leon was the bait.
- Bait?</font>

83
00:04:16,047 --> 00:04:17,299
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jesus?</font>

84
00:04:17,382 --> 00:04:18,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screaming]</font>

85
00:04:20,010 --> 00:04:22,804
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't ever! Dumb mother--!</font>

86
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:29,227
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're using Jesus to beat us up?
Have you seen <i>South Park?</i></font>

87
00:04:29,311 --> 00:04:33,815
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good call-out, Morty. That's the kind of meta I like,
the kind that keeps us creatively accountable.</font>

88
00:04:33,899 --> 00:04:35,776
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, God. Not the Bane. Not the Bane!</font>

89
00:04:35,859 --> 00:04:36,735
<font face="Serif" size="18">[shouts]</font>

90
00:04:37,444 --> 00:04:40,363
<font face="Serif" size="18">He Baned me, Morty. Oh, Jesus Baned me.</font>

91
00:04:41,364 --> 00:04:44,826
<font face="Serif" size="18">You can't beat me up.
I'm technically a Christian child!</font>

92
00:04:44,910 --> 00:04:49,122
<font face="Serif" size="18">And I'm your worst nightmare.
I'm the Jesus from every Jesus joke.</font>

93
00:04:49,206 --> 00:04:50,540
<font face="Serif" size="18">The one without a God.</font>

94
00:04:50,624 --> 00:04:52,209
<font face="Serif" size="18">Morty! Take this and get out!</font>

95
00:04:53,668 --> 00:04:58,590
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thank you. Looks like Story Lord's story
is about to become based on real events.</font>

96
00:04:58,673 --> 00:05:01,510
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What do you want with that?
- I want what any character wants.</font>

97
00:05:01,593 --> 00:05:02,886
<font face="Serif" size="18">Motivation.</font>

98
00:05:02,969 --> 00:05:05,388
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What? [burps] That's dumb.
- So lazy.</font>

99
00:05:05,472 --> 00:05:07,224
<font face="Serif" size="18">Forward your notes to my ass.</font>

100
00:05:09,518 --> 00:05:10,977
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, what? He just left.</font>

101
00:05:11,061 --> 00:05:14,564
<font face="Serif" size="18">Kind of makes you want to be
our unlikely ally, huh? Oh, I guess not.</font>

102
00:05:14,648 --> 00:05:16,149
<font face="Serif" size="18">[gasping]</font>

103
00:05:16,775 --> 00:05:19,236
<font face="Serif" size="18">[narrator] <i>Previously on</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Jesus Christ:</font>

104
00:05:19,903 --> 00:05:21,404
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Hey, I'm Jesus.
- I'm Mary.</font>

105
00:05:21,488 --> 00:05:22,864
<font face="Serif" size="18">- That's my mom's name.
- Stop.</font>

106
00:05:22,948 --> 00:05:26,159
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Dude, she's a hooker.
- She's a better disciple than you.</font>

107
00:05:26,701 --> 00:05:29,496
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ow! Oh! Ow!</font>

108
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:34,084
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, no. I can't die.</font>

109
00:05:34,167 --> 00:05:38,004
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I have a proposition for you.
- I work alone.</font>

110
00:05:38,088 --> 00:05:39,256
<font face="Serif" size="18">[roaring]</font>

111
00:05:40,757 --> 00:05:44,344
<font face="Serif" size="18">If I suck-a your blood,
I'll be invincible! I think.</font>

112
00:05:44,427 --> 00:05:46,137
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You'll never know.
- [screams]</font>

113
00:05:46,221 --> 00:05:50,308
<font face="Serif" size="18">Billionaire immortal entrepreneur Jesus Christ
has placed all his money</font>

114
00:05:50,392 --> 00:05:53,228
<font face="Serif" size="18">into what he's calling
a "second chance at love."</font>

115
00:05:53,311 --> 00:05:57,774
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Hang on, Mary!
- The data! So beautiful!</font>

116
00:05:57,858 --> 00:06:00,485
<font face="Serif" size="18">Make me normal, witch.</font>

117
00:06:01,111 --> 00:06:03,905
<font face="Serif" size="18">Take it all!</font>

118
00:06:03,989 --> 00:06:07,200
<font face="Serif" size="18">Eat your pudding, Mr. Christ.
What are you smiling at?</font>

119
00:06:07,284 --> 00:06:09,411
<font face="Serif" size="18">[chuckles] Your name.</font>

120
00:06:12,163 --> 00:06:13,290
<font face="Serif" size="18">What's happening, Rick?</font>

121
00:06:13,373 --> 00:06:15,667
<font face="Serif" size="18">Leon's venom makes
you think more and more of your life</font>

122
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,961
<font face="Serif" size="18">is behind you as he feeds
on your released potential.</font>

123
00:06:19,462 --> 00:06:22,090
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Leon, you saved our lives.
- Oh, not yet he hasn't.</font>

124
00:06:22,173 --> 00:06:25,552
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Jeez, Rick. So mean.
- He's meta, Morty. His life doesn't matter.</font>

125
00:06:25,635 --> 00:06:27,929
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yours does. That's why we need to get back.</font>

126
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,807
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, this doesn't feel like a citadel.</font>

127
00:06:32,934 --> 00:06:34,978
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe it's cooler on the inside.</font>

128
00:06:36,897 --> 00:06:38,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">This isn't what it looks like.</font>

129
00:06:38,315 --> 00:06:41,109
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is a very special diet
for successful writers.</font>

130
00:06:41,192 --> 00:06:43,904
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Why do you look like my character?
- I am your character.</font>

131
00:06:43,987 --> 00:06:46,281
<font face="Serif" size="18">And you are going to improve me.</font>

132
00:06:46,364 --> 00:06:49,868
<font face="Serif" size="18">- But you're Story Lord. You're great.
- Great isn't good enough!</font>

133
00:06:49,951 --> 00:06:55,123
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've killed Rick and made myself real!
I'm better than some shitty toy train.</font>

134
00:06:55,206 --> 00:06:59,002
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is this your office or your apartment?
Why does it smell like you sleep here?</font>

135
00:06:59,085 --> 00:07:02,130
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You're my creator. Why are you pathetic?
- Because you failed!</font>

136
00:07:02,213 --> 00:07:04,674
<font face="Serif" size="18">And whose fault is that?
What the hell happened?</font>

137
00:07:04,758 --> 00:07:06,843
<font face="Serif" size="18">You want to know what happened?
Specifically?</font>

138
00:07:06,927 --> 00:07:09,554
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, the Ricks wanted
to do a <i>Canterbury Tales</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">-type thing,</font>

139
00:07:09,638 --> 00:07:11,806
<font face="Serif" size="18">but none of them have read fucking
<i>Canterbury Tales.</i></font>

140
00:07:11,890 --> 00:07:14,935
<font face="Serif" size="18">They told me to make it like
the poker-game episode of the <i>Batman</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> cartoon</font>

141
00:07:15,018 --> 00:07:16,978
<font face="Serif" size="18">where the bad guys tell stories
about Batman.</font>

142
00:07:17,062 --> 00:07:20,899
<font face="Serif" size="18">Then they kept telling me it "needed something."
Yeah, no shit it needed something.</font>

143
00:07:20,982 --> 00:07:24,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">It needed to never be pitched! I did my job!</font>

144
00:07:24,194 --> 00:07:27,822
<font face="Serif" size="18">Goomby, the Ice Queen, the Tickets Please guy.
They just bailed on it!</font>

145
00:07:27,906 --> 00:07:29,491
<font face="Serif" size="18">The website didn't even fucking work!</font>

146
00:07:29,574 --> 00:07:33,161
<font face="Serif" size="18">And it was a shitty URL to begin with,
"Story-dash-train"?</font>

147
00:07:33,244 --> 00:07:36,706
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who uses a dash? They set me up to fail.
They fucked me!</font>

148
00:07:36,790 --> 00:07:39,584
<font face="Serif" size="18">They fucked me and you're lucky
I haven't blown my brains out!</font>

149
00:07:39,668 --> 00:07:42,253
<font face="Serif" size="18">Right. Just give me a motivation, you hacky fart.</font>

150
00:07:42,337 --> 00:07:45,590
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, here's your motivation.
You're looking for motivation.</font>

151
00:07:45,674 --> 00:07:48,802
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You want all the motivation.
- That's lazy.</font>

152
00:07:48,885 --> 00:07:51,221
<font face="Serif" size="18">It got you this far. Must be nice, by the way.</font>

153
00:07:51,304 --> 00:07:54,933
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wish I could afford to dress
like a bisexual acting coach from the '70s.</font>

154
00:07:55,016 --> 00:07:59,479
<font face="Serif" size="18">- My motivation is motivation.
- Okay. Bye.</font>

155
00:07:59,562 --> 00:08:03,024
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, no, my bitter friend. You're coming with me.</font>

156
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:08,029
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yo! if you don't see me coming,
it's a bad fortress!</font>

157
00:08:09,739 --> 00:08:12,659
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Where are we?
- Headquarters of the Self-Referential Six.</font>

158
00:08:12,742 --> 00:08:15,745
<font face="Serif" size="18">They're meta nerds that found out
they could be less bearable as a team.</font>

